HEADWORD: Usefulness
<hw>Use"ful*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
useful; utility; serviceableness; advantage.</def>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Utility; value; profit. See
<er>Utility</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Useless</ent>⟦br⟧
